recorditnow (Plugin based desktop recorder for KDE SC 4)

RecordItNow is a desktop recorder. Main features are:
Make screenshots. Automatically encode your videos in a desired format.
Zoom. Show mouse activity. Keyboard monitor. Timeline.
Upload your videos to YouTube or blip.tv.

Home: http://recorditnow.sourceforge.net/

